的孩子奇迹 (Miracle) 在乌干达坎帕拉的家中。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Esther Ruth Mbabazi/彭博社&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;世界银行向从非洲到亚洲的营利性设施投资了&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;数十亿纳税人的钱，&lt;/strong&gt;本应改善医疗保健的普及。但&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6Sa1VabqH5ZW_7aRy4suzlnM5z-tahoos4FhSbGds2cWK7PEAU0vC5TijUEP4hF8mF6v_8lozbDSBGZ5-xJ3Y5iX2rsqBhXXgNL4ZnASQ6Y_KlDdfRfRiCklngy2xBZaA0N4DAc9WjR76HmtmtV11ISSzWbnM4u4G14npPIQ8OfZz8dTL5zVytKg8ktbsefjbMmyfA9KuJegtew_31opCdnA37-vlGRgt83tlqg1o8GR6OzvZbe_yRH1VvZLWH9OjHfwXKR3qOIiymVt9pAhe3EBCBTY9GmPBqlU2GSUGqwKfCvcVFEHuEPAv5Iti89_RkA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;滥用追债策略&lt;/a&gt;或拒绝提供救生治疗的故事却层出不穷。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px 8px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="2"&gt;大事播客&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: #CCC; padding: 16px 8px 9px 0px; border: none;" valign="top" width="129"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SbIfB0-OukSDzwCbxSq9lYs3mZ56owPYjCTvdmZ1C2wI0KuBfvqLV47wJaXVH3K_3LItmjWBPPZpW1RVxAbZXs8DYn1dihLfuzM7W1ELleEREH6kud93d-EG6VGlJNpFBgwZsxPHXcP12QHI75_i_xtY9d-B1WB7WbiS-VbH7aAvzP485ZhmNZXmd8XRbaCge-8rDsrr0iGAuxiRdNrXtqgFmLf_D_Hg8sFw-pxOwbuWN8FRs5xQ8Pxu3MS88y8f8JANRSbBmWogTHddlnqn7IRIjSpU-ccXjdiYf6o2oGjfvzsF9cSNJFUWYp3lhmiAyQ%3D%3D" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none