ext-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;阅读故事&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)提名的美国财政部长&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;斯科特·贝森特(Scott Bessent)&lt;/strong&gt;在周四的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=411cfd5eb58b4f228c7f801d836a7c7a&amp;amp;_e=F2ROYGLVfvLK97R1ZPphK33uzg-0eo-2LVCkZHkRy2CxRM87FLIpT2yt7lNf9-bOV6-238MPkEJUwjoGfviGV4nMukQFNZhLHoaTugxSSiwYzyXXOGbAkf-yPLCppTUYSslg4RGoiUmB2A1ZL6uhnjOxBfS6yfAH00TdVrE_7WdVHfPnMj-4TWODqU-A7USwvivxyklKtjex9fruB95J8R-cold_cVZKDfyQ_HXpf5w%3D" target="_blank"&gt;参议院金融委员会听证&lt;/a&gt;会上面对议员们。贝森特尚未在联邦办公室任职，人们普遍预计他将在共和党控制的参议院获得确认。在整个听证会上，这位 62 岁的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=411cfd5eb58b4f228c7f801d836a7c7a&amp;amp;_e=F2ROYGLVfvLK97R1ZPphK9lPPfqbW9D74Ri8Nu-My9XzDS46p0dMSBrFQ-rt-gozk-YkZGgNWKhuxYy0q_DTeip3sFfI6uy2ZvJXMjdYcWdDgfmC77PZ2u974JlMG99_LIDumOSiv1B9mm6tut2PxOFBDN_QO04v4xRySEIR6PMpfvcSmYk951AWbN-X8PGoNygMPCllCn8r7CFkqj0HiyPU_j1o3DeSFpZ-9_d0r68%3D" target="_blank"&gt;对冲基金投资者&lt;/a&gt;兼经理表示，他支持加大对俄罗斯石油工业的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=411cfd5eb58b4f228c7f801d836a7c7a&amp;amp;_e=F2ROYGLVfvLK97R1ZPphK__xU2UEyMN0i6SrhpB2eEAmxYP2nZRcE0gHKwxsDU5x8Sn311C2-mzBLb1-jClMAg68pUDDgyBtS51PIc97frVWie6vt76ZuoSkbBRuEN5KDfKFm0DC6Z3ezy-m0IgUlAITMWsOdprO4Pn6b70VLKwPcYQo1APkSX_A__6Jm7TmJ1NhZnRhgJCaerGfFBQc8s6CIC3xyOlnWUPG3gBXMhc%3D" target="_blank"&gt;制裁力度&lt;/a&gt;，以结束乌克兰战争，并且正如预期的那样，强调&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=411cfd5eb58b4f228c7f801d836a7c7a&amp;amp;_e=F2ROYGLVfvLK97R1ZPphKy0sPz6PO0fQTPd5MjPYFzUSsCgg26_Nz7Pw3YpVrOqiBpxX6ciP7eUjrUM_fPXveJ0j0YyHEXqxdn-3j4V7OzQxz4JI1F8IOdxjxuB7fNUANfMXzhwR47RWpPSVjIG-CDCeHmDlN7Xljd3hHN3iA8BVWRxUQz-gyjhK6mYtr5dylVXtvLsJ7K7zpWQX-DC0WXgYlj2KZKbYDAI1DYS1D94%3D" target="_blank"&gt;维持美元&lt;/a&gt;作为世界货币的地位。储备货币对美国经济健康至关重要。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding-bottom: 18px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=411cfd5eb58b4f228c7f801d836a7c7a&amp;amp;_e=F2ROYGLVfvLK97R1ZPphK188mLDyrn2MIh7hpOiDtV71Aajzy94YEMAu0YlkXF-I2lNcEI3drX5PUJ-G7igKPb_S8L8okSwQBswmkp1h6Iop7NeEKUyeKgnWggyARDcu-Rmt1U3vjn9AXLWVGpYzj0B6bgmsnKzzcASqWF0N7pej4QlMKaRn2HadpFzCpaQDYTodiL-9G9edo4_BHwXp5QPi7sdl-rKl7Wg_EoaYlj8%3D" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQmqCB7cnXgM/v0/550x381.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; 